		<title>狗狗為何總是緊跟主人？揭開牠們行為背後的情感密碼</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/10/20/%e7%8b%97%e7%8b%97%e7%82%ba%e4%bd%95%e7%b8%bd%e6%98%af%e7%b7%8a%e8%b7%9f%e4%b8%bb%e4%ba%ba%ef%bc%9f%e6%8f%ad%e9%96%8b%e7%89%a0%e5%80%91%e8%a1%8c%e7%82%ba%e8%83%8c%e5%be%8c%e7%9a%84%e6%83%85%e6%84%9f/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[火報]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Mon, 20 Oct 2025 09:37:35 +0000</pubDate>
